      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:4:39:7",
      "relations": null,
      "text": [
        " قَضَى رَسُولُ اللَّهِ ( صلى الله عليه وآله ) فِي جَنِينِ الْهِلَالِيَّةِ حَيْثُ رُمِيَتْ بِالْحَجَرِ فَأَلْقَتْ مَا فِي بَطْنِهَا غُرَّةَ عَبْدٍ أَوْ أَمَةٍ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Al Nowfaly, from Al Sakuny, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Rasool-Allah<sup>saww</sup> judged regarding a foetus of Al-Hilaliya when she was pelted by a rock, so she miscarried what was in her belly, a compensation of a (male) servant, or a (female) servant’."
        ]
      }
    }
